---
title: Bacony French Onion Soup Burgers with Potato Wedges & a Garden Salad
description: Meet French onion soup—burger-fied! Yep, our chefs went and transformed everyone’s favorite cheese-topped soup into a bodacious burger. The two were basically meant to join forces, but in typical fashion, those chef-innovators went and took it to a whole new level. Think juicy all-beef patties topped with rich, thyme-flecked caramelized onions, crispy bacon, and a luscious cheese sauce. On the side, there’s lemony greens and crispy potato wedges (because it is still a burger after all). Bon appetit!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5e1e3d3d1ba087096711a1d2-37378f75.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/bacony-french-onion-soup-burgers-5e1e3d3d1ba087096711a1d2-853e9eb9.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/bacony-french-onion-soup-burgers-5e1e3d3d1ba087096711a1d2
time required: 45 minutes
cuisine: North America
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 1510 kcal
